nodes.text: An avian species lived in the jungles of the planet D'Qar.

The birds resided in nests high up in the jungle canopy, where they could hide their entire bodies, before the popped out their heads, which were nestled on long necks. The birds' two eyes stood upon stalks on their heads, covered in light blue feathers. They also had pinkish beaks, with which they could peck whatever fell or jumped into their vicinity.
